<li id="cite_note-51"><b><a href="#cite_ref-51" title="">^</a></b> Innis, Harold. (1951) <i>The Bias of Communication</i>. Toronto: University of Toronto Press, p. 87.</li>
<li id="cite_note-52"><b><a href="#cite_ref-52" title="">^</a></b> Innis (Bias), pp. 61–91. The comment about universities mustering their courage appears in "The upside of ivory towers" by Rick Salutin. <i>Globe and Mail</i>, September 7, 2007.</li>
<li id="cite_note-53"><b><a href="#cite_ref-53" title="">^</a></b> Creighton, p,84.</li>
